Class SubstitutionModification

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.core.SubstitutionModification

public class SubstitutionModification
extends java.lang.Object

Substitution Modification is a Modification where One amino acid is replaced by another amino acid. For example Deamidation Post-Translational Modification is a Substitution Modification where the amino acid Asparagine (N) is replaced by Aspartic Acid (D)
